is.erle.mavlink

Class Point3D

  • java.lang.Object
    • is.erle.mavlink.Point3D

  • public class Point3D
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a 3D point in space. It has all the functions to operate on a point like normalize, cross product, dot product , distance etc.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Version:
    %I%, %G%
    Author:
    Abhay Kumar
